    "description": "Once again take the role of <strong>Cakeboy</strong> in this sequel to <strong>Khimera: Destroy all Monster Girls</strong>' &quot;game-within-a-game&quot;. Run, jump, punch and use the variety of pastry-themed weapons at your disposal to blast through 9 action-packed stages. Face off against Cakeboy's eternal rival, the enigmatic <strong>Dark Cake</strong> and send him packing!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319580/extras/0bef407e9872cc51d41e9a6ea82f85b5.poster.avif?t=1680050003\" width=476 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319580/extras/0bef407e9872cc51d41e9a6ea82f85b5.webm?t=1680050003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319580/extras/0bef407e9872cc51d41e9a6ea82f85b5.mp4?t=1680050003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items no chef should leave at home:</h2>Pick up far-away items with the <strong>Croissant Boomerang</strong>, set traps with the exploding <strong>Cupcake Bomb</strong>, perform trick-shots with the bouncing <strong>Super Donut</strong>, or just punch them in the face! The choice is yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Short and Sweet:</h2>This snack-sized game's nine levels can be completed in about 20 minutes but hidden collectable ingredients, achievements and other secrets give you extra goals for subsequent play-throughs.",
